How to build the code
======================


This code uses FFTW (http://www.fftw.org/) to compute the FFT. I'm using FFT to get a improve the performance of 1-D variogram calculation[1].


References
----------

[1] Marcotte, D. Fast variogram computation with FFT. Computer & Geosciences. December 1996. Vol. 22. Issue 10. 1175â€“1186. 
